{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is Paws and Leaves?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Paws and Leaves, you play as Me, a young fox bitten by a snake and now... dying. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's like life flashing before your eyes, when you die. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll follow Me on his final journey to rediscover his memories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By his side is a charming butterfly named Ani, who will help you, sometimes more, sometimes less. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Me relies on his senses, like smelling, to locate his memories in the realm between life and death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During your journey, you'll encounter various characters, uncover their stories, and retrieve memories and keepsakes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Keepsakes aren't Me's memories; they're yours, the player's.</strong> They're scattered throughout the world and can be anything - a personal message, an image, or even a short video clip that you want to endure in our world.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through our <strong>Kickstarter</strong>, you'll have the opportunity to include one of your memories as an exclusive keepsake in the game. These submissions will become permanent collectibles, cherished and valued. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautiful, colorful seasons create a cute and cozy backdrop, while the poignant story and subtle &quot;jumpscares&quot; serve as a reminder: </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Me is fading. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paws and Leaves guides you through its narrative, yet allows you to explore the breathtaking world in-between. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Small &quot;open world&quot; zones invite you to discover more keepsakes, unravel their secrets, and unveil new tales. You can even fish for mementos on an old, wise turtle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This demo is our prototype demo and limited to ~25 minutes of gameplay. The story is quiet shorter than the exploration part.</h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Storytime","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/afd298036e4aff62fce8930a4d1d754ff33c8f70.jpg"},{"name":"Adventuretime","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/5a63e348e2964628284a694ba46061d0345f2419.jpg"},{"name":"A Snake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/afb96772f4499d31d714895b5bbdaefefd496256.jpg"},{"name":"An Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/ddcc6713a9ce586576e98c031e17dd00c2aa23e8.jpg"},{"name":"Holy Moly","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/7dfc9b97e9bf0b8d4cf7d464faa86d260425b4fe.jpg"},{"name":"See the world above","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/19bf01b3e6359794caacb98b8d7aec683f44df60.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta fish'em all","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/fa2a41fd8ae7d16907e8d644e01a6ee7f68839aa.jpg"},{"name":"Dark Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/cac0b02f97f6cf422c7d9b5f4ef21c90198453f8.jpg"},{"name":"A Beary Friendship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/05006d59234639f7e1d69aa1dee3fdb8336896d0.jpg"},{"name":"Me and You","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146130/43ec1f04a7712957e1c0478272c0cf345aa05464.jpg"}],"total":12},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728467875","background_ra